th=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-package w-5 h-5 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11 21.73a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73z\"></path><path d=\"M12 22V12\"></path><polyline points=\"3.29 7 12 12 20.71 7\"></polyline><path d=\"m7.5 4.27 9 5.15\"></path></svg></div><div><div class=\"font-display text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-900\">Midwest</div><div class=\"text-[0.65rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-brand-500\">Shipment Company</div></div></a><div class=\"hidden flex-1 items-center justify-center md:flex\"><nav class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6\"><a class=\"text-[0.8rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-700 transition hover:text-brand-500\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"text-[0.8rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-700 transition hover:text-brand-500\" href=\"/services\">Services</a><a class=\"text-[0.8rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-700 transition hover:text-brand-500\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"text-[0.8rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-700 transition hover:text-brand-500\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"text-[0.8rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-700 transition hover:text-brand-500\" href=\"/track\">Track Parcel</a></nav></div><div class=\"hidden items-center gap-3 md:flex\"><a class=\"rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-slate-900 transition hover:border-brand-400 hover:bg-slate-50\" href=\"/track\">Track Package</a><a class=\"rounded-full bg-brand-500 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-white transition hover:bg-brand-400\" href=\"/contact\">Get Quote</a></div><button type=\"button\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-3 text-white transition hover:bg-white/10 md:hidden\" aria-label=\"Toggle navigation menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></header><main><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden pt-32 pb-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl text-center\"><h1 class=\"text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-bold mb-6\">Get in Touch</h1><p class=\"text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto\">Questions about our services? Need a quote? Our team is ready to help with your logistics needs.</p></div></section><section class=\"px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-24\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16\"><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 backdrop-blur-xl\"><div class=\"inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-400 mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin h-6 w-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-3\">Address</h3><p class=\"text-slate-300 text-sm mb-1\">1450 Industrial Parkway</p><p class=\"text-slate-300 text-sm mb-1\">Columbus, Ohio, USA</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 backdrop-blur-xl\"><div class=\"inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-400 mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-phone h-6 w-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M13.832 16.568a1 1 0 0 0 1.213-.303l.355-.465A2 2 0 0 1 17 15h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2A18 18 0 0 1 2 4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-.8 1.6l-.468.351a1 1 0 0 0-.292 1.233 14 14 0 0 0 6.392 6.384\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-3\">Phone</h3><p class=\"text-slate-300 text-sm mb-1\">+1 (614) 555-0123</p><p class=\"text-slate-300 text-sm mb-1\">+1 (614) 555-0199</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 backdrop-blur-xl\"><div class=\"inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-400 mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock h-6 w-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-3\">Business Hours</h3><p class=\"text-slate-300 text-sm mb-1\">Mon-Fri: 6 AM – 8 PM ET</p><p class=\"text-slate-300 text-sm mb-1\">Sat: 8 AM – 4 PM ET</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-24\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl\"><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] bg-white/95 p-8 shadow-2xl backdrop-blur-xl ring-1 ring-slate-900/5 sm:p-10\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-slate-950 mb-8\">Send us a message</h2><form class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2\">Name *</label><input type=\"text\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-slate-900 placeholder-slate-400 focus:border-brand-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-100\" placeholder=\"Your name\" name=\"name\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2\">Email *</label><input type=\"email\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-slate-900 placeholder-slate-400 focus:border-brand-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-100\" placeholder=\"your@email.com\" name=\"email\" value=\"\"/></div></div><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2\">Phone</label><input type=\"tel\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-slate-900 placeholder-slate-400 focus:border-brand-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-100\" placeholder=\"+1 (555) 000-0000\" name=\"phone\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2\">Subject</label><select name=\"subject\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-slate-900 focus:border-brand-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-100\"><option value=\"\" selected=\"\">Select a subject</option><option value=\"Quote Request\">Quote Request</option><option value=\"Shipment Issue\">Shipment Issue</option><option value=\"General Inquiry\">General Inquiry</option><option value=\"Partnership\">Partnership</option></select></div></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2\">Message *</label><textarea name=\"message\" required=\"\" rows=\"6\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-slate-900 placeholder-slate-400 focus:border-brand-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-100\" placeholder=\"Tell us about your shipment needs...\"></textarea></div><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><button type=\"submit\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-600 px-8 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-brand-600/30 transition hover:bg-brand-500 disabled:opacity-50\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-send mr-2 h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M14.536 21.686a.5.5 0 0 0 .937-.024l6.5-19a.496.496 0 0 0-.635-.635l-19 6.5a.5.5 0 0 0-.024.937l7.93 3.18a2 2 0 0 1 1.112 1.11z\"></path><path d=\"m21.854 2.147-10.94 10.939\"></path></svg>Send Message</button><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/20 bg-white/10 px-8 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-white/20\" href=\"/track\">Track Shipment</a></div></form></div></div></section></main><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 pb-24 pt-20 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"mb-12 text-center\"><p class=\"section-subtitle text-brand-400\">Trusted by international partners</p><h2 class=\"text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl\">Customer testimonials from premium logistics clients</h2></div><div class=\"swiper space-y-8 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"swiper-wrapper\"><div class=\"swiper-slide\"><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/85 p-10 shadow-2xl backdrop-blur-xl text-white\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 